data.description: Lovely home nestled in desired area of Evergreen Park. This 5 bedroom , 2.5 bath home has been meticulously maintained. This home has hardwoods floors & updated spacious kitchen. The huge master bed includes a walk-in closet of your dreams.  There is plenty of room to spread out and grow, there is also a large finished basement with a cozy fireplace. The fenced yard offers a patio area and a detached 2.5 car garage with a side drive. The roof is 2020 & the AC was done in July of 2023. There's simply nothing to do here but move in and enjoy!! Nearby parks and schools as well. Come see it today!!
